product_name: Benefit CosmeticsGimme Brow+ Tinted Volumizing Eyebrow Gel Mini
summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsSustainable PackagingBenefit Cosmetics Gimme Brow+ Tinted Volumizing Eyebrow Gel is an award-winning, innovative brush-on gel containing tiny micro fibers that adhere to skin and hair, creating full, lush-looking brows where before there were none. In a travel-size mini!
details: DetailsBenefitsTravel-size miniVolumizes, tames & tints browsNatural-looking & buildableWater-resistant & long-wearingFeatures94% said brows looked visibly thicker**Self-evaluation by 66 women after 1 weekItem 2536843How To UseInstant brow FULLfillment! Thin brows? Skimpy brows? Solved! Using short pressing motions, stroke the precision tip brush along your brows to define shape & add instant volume. Comb through to blend & build natural-looking fullness.Beauty Tip: Start your look with Benefit's bestselling precisely, my brow pencil for expertly full & defined brows!IngredientsAqua (Water), Mica, Glyceryl Stearate, Polypropylene, Magnesium Aluminum Silicate, PEG-100 Stearate, Polyacrylamide, Phenethyl Alcohol, C13-14 Isoparaffin, Glyceryl Caprylate, Laureth-7, Panthenol, Glycerin, Silica, Althaea Officinalis Root Extract, Citric Acid, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate. May Contain: CI 19140 (Yellow 5, Yellow 5 Lake), CI 42090 (Blue 1 Lake), CI 77000 (Aluminum Powder), CI 77007 (Ultramarines), CI 77163 (Bismuth Oxychloride), CI 77288 (Chromium Oxide Greens), CI 77289 (Chromium Hydroxide Green), CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), CI 77510 (Ferric Ferrocyanide, Ferric Ammonium Ferrocyanide), CI 77742 (Manganese Violet), CI 77891 (Titanium Dioxide)Product ingredient listings are updated periodically. Comb through to blend & build natural-looking fullness.Beauty Tip: Start your look with Benefit's bestselling precisely, my brow pencil for expertly full & defined brows!

reviews.headline: Where is just WARM AUBURN 2.75?!??????
reviews.comments: Benefit Cosmetics, I am thoroughly disappointed in the new line of colors for your amazing volumizing brow gel. I purchased the Warm Auburn BROWN 3.5 thinking it would work, but it is entirely too dark. I do not understand why you still have the 2.75 in the brow pencil and pen products, and the brow wax, but not the gel. Sadly, I am going to be returning this wonderful product because it is not a viable option, and you no longer carry a color to match us redheads- it is either blonde or brown-no inbetween. I am just going to have to go back to my tried and true Clinique cause it never lets me down! Thank you for the several years with the best brows everrrr!!!!!!!

reviews.headline: Love this
reviews.comments: Grey Looks more natural with my grey hair. Make sure you dab the excess off on the opening area to prevent clumps.

reviews.headline: Love this
reviews.comments: I love the grey as it looks more natural with my hair. Make sure you dub off any excess on the opening area so it isn't too think when first applied.

reviews.headline: Good Overall.
reviews.comments:
Recently got this, and I like it! It definitely smooths my brows, adds color, and defition to them! And while I will say, it's a great product overall, it does have downsides.
For me it does not stay, hold my brows and it is a bit clumpy. it wears off by the end of the day and cannot handle sweat. Plus it's hard to get into the small details of your brows.
 I'd definitely say it is good, but take into consideration the downsides of it, before buying, because it's definitely pricey üò¨
Overall, it's good for light brows, and beginners! ü©∑

reviews.headline: Perfect color
reviews.comments: Perfect color. Easy to use and shape your eyebrows.  Color is fabulous for blond. Lots of times other products turn or look gray. This product delivers true color. My favorite brow product.

reviews.headline: Love This Long Lasting Product!
reviews.comments: Purchased the Medium shade in the  mini size. I am 72, fair skinned, with ash blond hair streaked with silver, gray, and white, especially in the front. My eyebrows are very thin, due to over plucking years ago with a mix of brown and white hairs. I lightly draw in the shape I want with my eye brow pencil, and then apply the GB gel in short vertical strokes. I HAVE BROWS AGAIN! Everything I've tried has not hedged up in the VERY humid Louisiana and Alabama heat, which often goes above 100 degrees! I can go about my day with workouts, errands, dog walks, and my brows NO LONGER melt! Thanks Benefit !

reviews.headline: I Have BROWS!
reviews.comments:
I have tried various brow makeup over the last few years.  I'm not quite sure but as I aged my eyebrows just seemed to disappear.  On a trip to ULTA with my granddaughter I noticed a display with eyebrow gel.  An associate asked if I would like to try it.  She applied it and I loved it.  It looks so natural and the color was a great match with my skin tone.  The small size is great for travel and the product stays put.

Thank you.

reviews.headline: Love it, just what I was looking for!
reviews.comments: Thank you Ramie for your excellent service! You were so helpful!

reviews.headline: Dried out
reviews.comments: Next time I'll buy the full-size product. I think it was dry because of the size.

reviews.headline: Finding a grey/gray was fabulous
reviews.comments: Finally a product that goes with my very white gray hair!! It matches my still dark brunette strands blended into my white hair. No golden taupe brown tints per usual brow enhancers. Very satisfied with purchase & will buy again. The Ulta rep, Marilyn,  in Flowood MS location gets credit for suggesting I try the Benefit brand.

reviews.headline: The only brow product I can trust!
reviews.comments: Stays put through every challenging day!

reviews.headline: nice product
reviews.comments: great for adding color to your brows and shaping them however this product made my eyebrows too dark for my preference and it can be hard to find the right amount to apply.

reviews.headline: I would buy again
reviews.comments: Really like it

reviews.headline: I love the way this brow paste works!
reviews.comments: So easy to use! It works just amazingly!

reviews.headline: Amazing brow gel
reviews.comments: This is my absolute favorite brow gel in combination with the benefit micro precise brow pencil. Packaging is convenient and it lasts all day.

reviews.headline: One and done brow product
reviews.comments: I have been using this product for almost a month and I'm really pleased. I don't need any other products or multiple steps. I just brush it on and go. Very beginner friendly and lasts for a long time after application.  I fear I'm only going to be able to use high quality now that I've started out that way. Will repurchase.

reviews.headline: Wish it coated coarse gray eyebrow hairs better.
reviews.comments: As I age my eyebrows are becoming more gray, so it appears that they are thin when they are not. Love the number of shades available. Applies nicely and stays put. After application, my brows have a nice, full and natural appearance. But the product doesn't apply well to gray hair. I have to really "work it" a lot to have it finally cover some of the gray. I have tried other brands, and have had similar or worse results regarding the gray brow hair - so to date, this is the best I have used so far.

reviews.headline: I will buy this again
reviews.comments: This eyebrow product in my opinion is way better than pencils or any other product Ive used to color my eyebrows.

faceoff_positive.comments:
I was a bit hesitant to try this product because I didn't quite believe the hype, but I'm so glad I dedited to try it out.

I love this stuff. I have hardly any eyebrows from constantly plucking since I was 9(I'm in my mid 20's now). I've tried to let them grow out for a few years, and they are super sparse and all over the place now. They simply don't seem to grow in some areas.
So I thought, this probably won't work for me. I've been drawing my eyebrows on since I was 9 years old (because I'd over-pluck), and tried all sorts of products including, more recently, eyebrow products with little mascara style brushes like this. They would dry and look ridiculous.

Anyway, this stuff looks suuuuper natural. I bought this along with the pencil. I use this first to fill in my brows and then the pencil to make them look sharper where needed.
Even my boyfriend said they looked super natural. They do, and this is exactly what I've been looking for for years.

I should mention, this isn't waterproof -which is fine;I haven't seen anything in descriptions saying it was..though for the price, I would like it a lot more if it were. I will just be using Model in a Bottle to make it waterproof.

The only other thing I noticed is that there doesn't seem to be much product in the container. Again, ideally, for the price I would hope for a little more, but it is what it is and it does work wonderfully so can't complain too much.

Lastly, I ordered this in the darkest shade, which is cool toned. I'm pretty cool-neutral, and have dark hair, so it works great for me. However, I do wonder how this would work on someone with much darker skin than mysel, as well as those with lighter, cooler toned hair. More 
shades should definitely be made. 

Other than that, this stuff is wonderful and I'm super happy with it. I'm very self conscious about having sparse brows and my brows clearly looking very artificial, so I'll be using this as long as it's available.
faceoff_positive.headline: Very helpful product

I received a sample of this product from a friend and I absolutely loved it.... until I ordered it and saw how small this product is and I was shocked! For the price you are paying this product is SO SMALL!! Honestly, I thought I I received a travel sized one by mistake until I realized that this is the "regular size" for this product. 

NOT WORTH THE PRICE and this is coming from someone who normally doesn't mind spending a ton of money on makeup
